 <p>
  <b>Rule-15 ᐅ </b>
  Determine/arrange/be determined/demand/decide/ be anxious, etc.+ infinitive + object-যুক্ত active voice-এর passive কাঠামো ᐅ 
 </p>
 <card>Active voice-এর subject+ মূল verb+ that+ infinitive -এর পরের object+ should be+ infinitive-কে verb-এ পরিণত করে তার past participle.</card>
 <h3>Example ᐅ </h3>
 <ul>
  <li>He decided to prepare the proposal. (Active)</li>
  <li>He decided that the proposal should be prepared. (Passive)</li>
 </ul>
